title: PG Music - The Pianist Series
description: The Pianist Series is a set of Music Programs containing a huge collection of over 900 of the world's most popular piano pieces, performed by world-class pianists. Plus... Music Trivia Game, "Guess the Song", Program Notes, Biographies, Music Dictionary (all on disk).... and much more. On-screen piano keyboard lets you see the music as it's played. Learn the music by watching the on-screen keyboard or slowing down the performance. Other functions: Stop/Pause/Rewind/Slow Motion/Tempo Changes/Transposition/Volume/Velocity
